itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/4/2022. 

Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio for the second time in the New Year! Congratulations You Played Yourself is handed out to Ebro and a couple other people, DJ John snitches on Ebro, Ebro snitches on Rosenberg on IG Live, and Laura Stylez brings you the biggest news in Flashing Lights.
